overview: She’s Got A Plan directed by and starring Fatima Washington, follows Isis  Angelo,  a struggling female writer-director who gives herself an ultimatum: either make her dream career take off in 30 days or throw in the towel for good. But, will she be able to go against everything she believes to become something she’s always wanted to be?
tagline: It's Time To Call All The Shots!
title: She's Got a Plan
